• Filter the fields.

• Grouping the fields.

• User wants to check the permissions for an Administrator.
• User wants to check the permissions for a Moderator.
• User wants to check the permissions for a Contributor.
• User wants to check the permissions for an Observer.
7. *Make Functional Test for the Configuration* 
• Change the Visibility of a field(s) in the Configuration App. 
• Relabel a field(s) in the Configuration App. 
• Configure template in the Configuration App.
8. *Make Functional Test for the Send action*
9. *Make Functional Test for the View action*
10. *Make Functional Test for the History action*
• History / View and Hide.
• History / View the complete.
• History / View the related records.

• Compile
